latestIgtvVideos.title: Daytime smokey eyes in 8 simple steps
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Confession... before @studio10makeup sent me their Visible Lift Radiance palette I’d never tried a smokey eye (I know I can’t believe it either!) Now I’m a covert. The blend of colours really opens up my eyes and I love the autumnal brown tones.  I’m a ‘less is more’ girl so the lighter shading works well for me but you could easily build it up for a darker evening look. I’m also loving the shade and define brushes and the 6 in 1 double ended mascara. Plus all of the products are designed for mature skin and if you use code TGWTB10 there’s 10% off everything...
.
All the products are linked below. Any questions please shout. It’s my first make up IGTV and I’m no make up pro so apologies for the strange faces and poor technique. Definitely a work in progress but if I can create a smokey eye anyone can! #thatgirlwiththebob...
.

Happy Sunday my lovelies! Today I’m taking part in the #twopointsixchallenge to raise money for UK charities who are losing an estimated £4 billion due to the London marathon being cancelled because of CV-19. Anyone can get involved - all you need to do is think of activity based around the number 26 or 2.6 - it could be anything - eating 26 of something, walking, running, skipping 2.6km, learning 26 words in another language, 26 laps of your garden or stairs. Anything goes. I’ll pop more info on stories along with my challenge and I’ll be donating money to @the_bhf @thestrokeassociation @cr_uk and @smiletrainuk all charities close to my heart. #thatgirlwiththebob...
.

latestPosts.caption:
This is 50! 🎂 A brilliant weekend celebrating in Seville with my hubby & then back home yesterday evening for cuddles with my girls, my daughter’s lush homemade birthday cake & pressies. 

Totally blown away by a video they made for  me which was shot over the last decade with family & friends saying Happy Birthday. Seeing my girls tiny faces, people saying happy birthday to me on their wedding days & birthdays - just wow - the thought & planning is unbelievable. I’m honestly lost for words, and crying just writing this, the best present ever. #thatgirlwiththebob 

PS - couldn’t resist the hotel balcony 🪭 reel. Wanted it to be one of those cool girl balcony shots but neither of us could lean far enough out & I’m just not a cool girl 😂
